we had it made ¶

00:12.778 --> 00:15.981
[ together ]
¶ those were the days ¶

00:16.047 --> 00:19.317
[ Edith ]
¶ and you knew
where you were then ¶

00:19.384 --> 00:23.354
[ Archie ]
¶ girls were girls
and men were men ¶

00:23.422 --> 00:25.690
[ Archie, Edith ]
¶ mister, we could use a man ¶

00:25.758 --> 00:29.661
