00:56.956 --> 00:58.890
Hi, daddy.
<i>Hi.</i>

00:58.958 --> 01:03.628
- Hi, arch. How's the world
treatin' you today?
- Don't start up with me.

01:03.696 --> 01:07.766
Oh, here he is,
the good humor man.

01:07.833 --> 01:10.769
- Have a pleasant day, arch?
- Yeah, beautiful.

01:10.836 --> 01:14.505
Comin' home I was held up
31 minutes in that subway train.

01:14.573 --> 01:18.342
Packed in like sardines, we was:
No lights, no fans,

01:18.410 --> 01:23.347
me crushed up against
a 300-pound Italian,
half of which was pure garlic.

01:25.417 --> 01:29.087
What a city. That Lindsay
can't do nothin' right.

